{"_id":"0HZxJzkuCLIY5LKi","name":"Crit Table DN: Devils and Demons","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"RollTable.2R7YHMsAX5Pnkchv"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/devil-mask.svg","description":"","results":[{"_id":"SdtEoh15aTtLNEWP","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Piercing blow. The character takes an additional [[/roll 1d8]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-500,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"prF5xXv6ShGB6A79","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Life burn. The character permanently loses an additional 2 hit points.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"AMEUQo8qArPoJRph","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Head strike. The character takes an additional [[/roll 1d10]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Rs8NSYlSxJtDHbwT","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Major life burn. The character permanently loses an additional 4 hit points.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"nOuC1ckpbunOw4if","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Corruption. Character takes on corruption, similar to a wizard casting spells. Roll [[/roll 1d10]] on a corruption table. If the demon has 5 HD or less, use the minor corruption table; if 6-10 HD, use the major corruption table; if 11+ HD, use  the greater corruption table.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"aX01AHGJWDS8fMWT","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Aging. The character ages [[/roll 1d10]] years instantly. If cumulative aging from this and other effects exceeds 20 years, the character suffers a -1 penalty to all physical ability scores.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"0RRr80WCViWBjIb6","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Infernal weakening I. The PC loses [[/roll 1d4]] points of ability score for one week. Determine randomly: (roll [[/roll 1d5]]) (1) Strength, (2) Agility, (3) Stamina, (4) Intelligence, (5) Personality.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"5YYYfcqZJp5Y1uoF","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Soul wound. The character loses 1 XP from the soul-burning touch of the demon.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"YiEIfUzvbbw4Vwoj","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Soul trade. The character’s soul is swapped with that of a soul already owned by the demon. The demon takes possession of the character’s soul while his body is now controlled by another life force. The character’s physical stats  remain unchanged, but re-roll the character’s new Intelligence, Personality, and Luck with [[/roll 3d6]]. The character loses all his normal memories and takes on the memories of the soul now in his body, including its most recent memories of infernal brimstone. He retains his class abilities and other training, but his new mental statistics may change the skill with which he uses his abilities. The character can recover his stolen soul only by journeying to the demon’s home plane and recovering it. The judge is encouraged to come up with a new history for the soul now in his body.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false},{"_id":"zRTuhmZlj6XAcYcD","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Double corruption! The PC takes on corruption twice, similar to a wizard casting spells. Roll [[/roll 1d10]] twice on a corruption table. If the demon has 5 HD or less, use the minor corruption table; if 6-10 HD, use the major corruption table;  if 11+ HD, use the greater corruption table.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false},{"_id":"KTSPWIvn75OQCoic","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Infernal weakening II. The PC loses 1 point of one ability score permanently. Determine randomly: (roll [[/roll 1d5]]) (1) Strength, (2) Agility, (3) Stamina, (4) Intelligence, (5) Personality.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Y1VVoskW3ic5HsWV","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Luck burn. The touch of the demon brings bad luck upon the character! He loses 1 point of Luck. A halfling or thief can recover this loss through normal class means.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"pwt640iJrl7QfwOc","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Severe soul wound. The character loses 3 XP from the demon’s soul-searing touch.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"qE3SHOmgUCr87jy7","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Astral drift. The character’s soul is sent adrift on the astral plane! The character drops to the ground, catatonic, and cannot be revived until his soul is located and returned to his body.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Ja8RM1EbSCjEwG1K","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Confinement. The demon’s strike breaks the magic bonds holding it on this plane and confines the character to the demon’s current location. The character sees a burning circle of flame appear around him, sputtering black with dark energy. The circle is approximately 5 feet in diameter and traps the character within. It is considered powerful magic (treat as spell check 25 to dispel). The character cannot pass through it by any means until it is dispelled or the  character is freed or “banished” back to his native free state. The demon, on the other hand, is now freed from any confinement or banishment to this plane and can return to its home plane at will.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false},{"_id":"XokkxhUHhmua7z0y","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Banishment. The demon’s strike banishes the character to the demon’s home plane! The character vanishes from sight as he is instantly transported back to the demon’s home. For all intents and purposes, the character is out of the game unless his allies immediately follow to save him.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[16,500],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d16","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"1NIawYOcDNXjgJDO","name":"Crit Table I: All 0-Level Characters and All Wizards","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"RollTable.eCI0rwPspM0rnaPD"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/farmer.svg","description":"","results":[{"_id":"8mrL4UZ3PSExmz37","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Force of blow shivers your weapon free of your grasp. Inflict +[[/roll 1d6]] damage with this strike and you are disarmed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[0,0],"drawn":false},{"_id":"QPnwoYM8JEQm2NP9","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Opportunistic strike. Inflict +[[/roll 1d3]] damage with this strike.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"W9qrYVO5dtTNHV4x","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe jabbed in the eye! Ugly bruising and inflict +[[/roll 1d4]] damage with this strike.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"FZX4DNzMOHTID3rR","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Stunning crack to forehead. Inflict +[[/roll 1d3]] damage with this strike, and the foe falls to the bottom of the initiative count next round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"eNQPSvWuWJSd8jz4","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to foe’s kneecap. Inflict +[[/roll 1d4]] damage with this strike and the foe suffers a -10’ penalty to speed until healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"8erK73kfyJvLtSza","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Solid strike to torso. Inflict +[[/roll 1d6]] damage with this strike.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"9Y0VMeDrYpklohcN","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lucky strike disarms foe. You gain a free attack if the enemy stoops to retrieve his weapon.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"LiNZuXIIG9E4HyYR","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Smash foe’s hand. Inflict +[[/roll 2d3]] damage with this strike. You break two of the enemy’s fingers.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"eAoiDHtoSrBUPUH5","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Numbing strike! Cursing in agony, the foe is unable to attack next round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Q3FYzWz7H4vblGlK","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Smash foe’s nose. Inflict +[[/roll 2d4]] damage with this strike and blood streams down the enemy’s face.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false},{"_id":"9Uwc0VrYf9rxqOhk","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe trips on his own feet and falls prone for the remainder of the round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false},{"_id":"2a2chpDfB4Hooo8L","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Piercing strike. Inflict +[[/roll 2d4]] damage with this strike.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"yZGWzMR63hONt0aB","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to groin. The foe must make a DC 15 Fort save or spend the next two rounds retching.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"ZHOASOYIZrlMLc0W","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow smashes foe’s ankle; his movement speed is reduced by half.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"X0nOXfjXtuagIwdu","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike grazes temple; blood blinds the foe for [[/roll 1d3]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false},{"_id":"YddMFp8oKSJw9JTz","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Stab enemy’s weapon hand. The weapon is lost and knocked [[/roll 1d10+5]] feet away.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false},{"_id":"NOF14rbxyjhz3Y5G","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Narrowly avoid foe’s counterstrike! Inflict normal damage and make another attack roll. If the second attack hits, you inflict an additional +[[/roll 1d6]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false},{"_id":"PPtRJQr56w8p6QWA","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow to throat. Foe staggers around for 2 rounds and is unable to speak, cast spells, or attack.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Pdf9nW4b4oqPppZ1","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe falls into your attack. He takes +[[/roll 2d6]] damage from the strike and curses your luck.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false},{"_id":"QqStR3g8CPMSX1p2","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Miracle strike. The foe must make a DC 20 Fort save or fall unconscious.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"fdZq345aDSEefNKh","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lucky blow dents foe’s skull! Inflict +[[/roll 2d6]] damage with this strike. If the foe has no helm, he suffers a permanent loss of [[/roll 1d4]] Int.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[20,500],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d21","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"5FkQKJqgH8E2Yj49","name":"Crit Table V: Level 5+ Warriors, and Level 6+ Dwarves","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dcc-compendiums.dcc-criticial-hit-tables.UlrAGj8utPn43OMN"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/barbarian.svg","description":"","results":[{"_id":"GLtPjoYD2dFIRLqB","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Battle rage makes friend and foe indistinguishable. Foe is hit for +[[/roll 3d8]] damage, and the ally nearest him is also hit by a rebounding blow for [[/roll 1d4]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-500,0],"drawn":false},{"_id":"EmpSNkGqjH3fN1xU","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe’s weapon shattered.* If the foe has no weapon, inflict +[[/roll 3d12]] damage with this strike","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"dSF6qjabzjZ0PNmW","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Furious assault hurls foe back [[/roll 1d10]]’. Any adjacent foes accidentally strike the target for damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"7rXNjNzrl5Vm0rUY","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow to skull destroys ear. Inflict +[[/roll 1d12]] damage with this strike, and the foe suffers permanent deafness","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"KgwPejxawtu9K30N","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to gut! The foe must make a Fort save (DC 20 + PC level) or spend the next 2 rounds retching bile from a ruptured stomach.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"9HqIDYloyqAl8bmg","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe casts weapon away and wails for mercy. Inflict +[[/roll 1d12]] damage with this strike and make another attack","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"ms9zstExvWPQ9rEq","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike scalps foe. Blood courses down his face, and the foe is effectively blinded until healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Eu8Ok4qjrNdAiGzo","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe entangled on your weapon, reducing his AC by -6 while caught. Make another attack.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"jAO2B6HDuTG4UAcQ","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"You see red! Inflict +[[/roll 1d12]] damage with this strike as you are overcome by battle rage!**","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[8,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"pDdspfCapeNDixXK","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to weapon arm. Foe takes quadruple damage from his own weapon as it is hammered into his face. Foe drops weapon in dumbfounded awe.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[13,14],"drawn":false},{"_id":"uTvsZ9BS1Wnj5Y8T","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow sunders shield. Inflict +[[/roll 2d12]] damage with this strike. If the foe has no shield, he must make a Fort save (DC 20 + PC level) or be knocked unconscious from the pain.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false},{"_id":"IxWnahb83E5MdReM","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Target is disemboweled, spilling his entrails onto the ground. Foe dies instantly of shock.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"uKCk3zwiERHMmF0R","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow destroys target’s face. Foe is immediately rendered blind and deaf and is now capable of only wet, gurgling sounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false},{"_id":"8APPUpOAIh6fGhfO","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike removes crown of target’s skull. Foe dies from exposed brain matter in [[/roll 3d3]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"ClVQxiyw8cTu8Uhn","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow severs shield arm. Inflict +[[/roll 2d12]] damage with this strike. Foe’s hopes of two-handed weapon mastery dashed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false},{"_id":"3QwfcPLrtjDwDub7","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Godly attack. Inflict +[[/roll 3d12]] damage with this strike. If the target dies, move up to 10’ and make another attack on any foe within 10’.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[21,21],"drawn":false},{"_id":"MalQ5EiZk5Lze68c","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow severs leg. Inflict +[[/roll 2d12]] damage with this strike, and the foe’s movement drops to zero. Foe does nothing but wail in agony for [[/roll 1d4]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[22,22],"drawn":false},{"_id":"3B1fDGqadYNwYQyG","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to skull stuns foe for [[/roll 1d4+1]] rounds and permanently reduces Int by [[/roll 1d12]]. Make another attack on your inert foe.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[23,23],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wu2rJqk7Ih2WZVEY","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike severs weapon arm. Inflict +[[/roll 2d12]] damage with this strike, and the foe is disarmed, literally and figuratively.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[24,24],"drawn":false},{"_id":"TgkSNZrvRvnHXPmU","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Devastating strike to torso voids foe’s bowels and crushes organs into paste. Foe loses 50% of current hit points and all dignity.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[25,25],"drawn":false},{"_id":"2V3T8mTHsVpc3b7n","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike crushes throat. Foe begins drowning in his own blood and expires in [[/roll 1d4]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[26,26],"drawn":false},{"_id":"PkVAryZKNF8XAFfG","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Crippling blow to spine. Inflict +[[/roll 4d12]] damage with this strike, and the foe suffers permanent paralysis","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[27,27],"drawn":false},{"_id":"E4H3eCsXoyUvG0TF","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe decapitated with a single strike. You are Death incarnate. Continue to make attacks against any foes within 10’ until you miss.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[28,500],"drawn":false},{"_id":"kbFWbtLD8AT9NDwe","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to top of skull shortens spinal column, shortening foe by 6”. Resulting nerve damage reduces foe’s AC by -4","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"64gdM60fGHs7Avbk","name":"Crit Table U: Un-dead","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"RollTable.9CGSzUEvy8tGacVp"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/raise-zombie.svg","description":"","results":[{"_id":"Cqeh34rq0nZHoqvO","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Unnatural boils sprout spontaneously around the wound. These are extremely painful to the touch, and automatically inflict 1 point of damage in any round where the character exerts himself physically (such as running, jumping, and  fighting). The boils can only be healed with magical healing.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-500,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wP7O1Urv0uV9sjbd","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The cold touch of un-death spreads across the wound. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d4]] damage and the PC gets the chills, chattering his teeth noisily until magically healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"0je2x40414vDpTMf","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The numbness of death spreads around the wounded area. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d4]] damage and the PC slowly loses sensation. On the next round, he must make a Fort save against DC 2. Failure means he is paralyzed. This first save is easy, but he must make another save against DC 3 on the next round, then against DC 4, then DC 5, and so on. If he makes every save to DC 20, he shakes off the numbness and is unaffected. If a single save is failed, the PC is paralyzed— he is insensitive to any sensation and completely numb and unable to move. The paralysis can be cured by any magical healing.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"tmJjniRw3CImoJPz","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The horrifying visage of life after death infects the PC’s thoughts as the un-dead leers into his eyes with its attack. The PC must make a DC 15 Fort save or be shaken and unable to move or attack for the next [[/roll 1d4]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"lGbIElxLuRzthJFX","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The character is cursed from beyond the grave! Depending on his actions and the intelligence of the undead creature, the curse may have specific terms associated with the wishes of the un-dead (judge’s discretion; see Appendix C).  Alternately, the curse causes a -1 penalty to Luck and all dice rolls until lifted.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"zIdOPLgpfpDZeWbp","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The wound blackens immediately and a horrid infection from beyond the grave begins to spread. The character must make a DC 10 Fort save or temporarily lose [[/roll 1d4]] Stamina. The infection continues to attack each day, forcing another DC 10  Fort save each morning (failure results in the loss of another [[/roll 1d4]] Stamina) until the infection is magically expunged. The character does not heal while infected.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"2XauddYdydovDfBX","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Supernatural frost spreads out from the wound in a lacy web, causing an additional [[/roll 1d8]] damage and intense pain. The frost dissipates on the next round but until the next full moon, the PC takes an extra 1 point of damage from all cold-based attacks.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"p7rUufgvuz5nkkyH","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Necrotic energies leap from the un-dead in a sizzling flash, enervating the character. The PC loses [[/roll 2d4]] Stamina temporarily.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"8lp298MH5TIS4aq3","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Faced with the very real prospect of unnatural un-death, the PC becomes unhinged. He immediately loses [[/roll 1d4]] Personality and goes temporarily insane, behaving erratically and strangely until the next new moon. The controlling player must make a percentile roll before any action, and on 01-10 the character makes an insane action (as determined by the judge) instead of what was intended. On 11-00 the intended action occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false},{"_id":"CSNepduwGpc4Mww0","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The visage of rotting un-death brings the horror of the grave to the character’s thoughts. He must make a DC 16 Fort save or be shaken with fear, unable to attack or do anything except quake in fear for [[/roll 1d4]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false},{"_id":"1BbmIMX3jTHE9A2V","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strange electrical sparks leap from the attacking un-dead, causing an additional [[/roll 1d10]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"E6cEjhHPWG7uBHZk","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The attack is imbued with some unnatural remnant of un-dead slumber. The character must make a DC 16 Fort save or fall asleep, instantly and deeply. He will not awaken for [[/roll 1d7]] hours or until shaken violently.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"LpbszxZQKx4ON3fi","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The attack is infused with powerful necromantic energies which cause the character’s skin to flake and rot! His flesh begins to fall off in large chunks, exposing the muscle and bone below. This is extremely painful and debilitating. The character loses an extra [[/roll 1d8]] hit points and 1 point of Personality immediately and again every morning thereafter as his flesh slowly rots. He dies when his Personality reaches 0. The rot can be arrested only by powerful magical healing.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"hafd2zJsW5PaCaF0","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The strike of un-death saps the PC’s energy. The character temporarily loses [[/roll 1d4]] Str and must make a DC 12 Fort save or lose an additional [[/roll 1d4]] Str.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false},{"_id":"af1dxrpTI8QyzYzh","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strange spectral energies arc to the PC’s body, making him temporarily incorporeal for [[/roll 1d4]] rounds. The PC cannot grasp physical objects. He cannot speak, make noise, attack, or be seen in bright light. He can fly at his normal movement rate and can pass through solid objects at half speed. He is considered un-dead while incorporeal. There is a 1% chance the transition is permanent.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Ce345VgCiYQzVl5T","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"A disgusting grave rot immediately spreads around the wound, causing an additional [[/roll 2d6]] damage and forcing a DC 16 Fort save. Failure on the save causes an additional temporary loss of [[/roll 1d4]] Stamina. The rot gets progressively worse until magically cured, forcing another save each morning against the loss of another [[/roll 1d4]] Stamina.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false},{"_id":"yiIwojc9xbO8xLfJ","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The brief brush with death affects the PCs’ memory. He loses all memory of the last 24 hours and must make a DC 16 Fort save or also lose memories of the past [[/roll 1d7]] days.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"QXJGVG8bXJbuBBDw","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The blow smashes against the PC’s temple and gives him a glimpse of his own death sometime in the future. This brush with death paralyzes the PC with fear for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false},{"_id":"i6izPHfqQNmvpP6k","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The wound immediately turns a deep yellow color and a dizzying madness infects the character. He temporarily loses [[/roll 1d6]] Intelligence and [[/roll 1d6]] Personality.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"qFPQyQ4ydTDP0QFw","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The wound takes the shape of an unholy mark. The character takes an additional [[/roll 1d6]] damage and is marked. Un-dead creatures are attracted to the PC from miles around. He cannot hide from un-dead, and they relentlessly hound him. The mark can only be removed by a blessing, holy cleansing, exorcism, or the like.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false},{"_id":"JO6pGRoGecFL3AE2","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The character’s soul is scarred by un-death. He permanently loses 1 point of Luck.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[21,21],"drawn":false},{"_id":"FxHJRk3ul7B64n2C","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The wound erupts in a disgusting infestation of maggots. They cause an additional [[/roll 2d6]] damage plus an ongoing [[/roll 1d6]] damage per round until the wound is healed via magical means.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[22,22],"drawn":false},{"_id":"A456gdLZgOFrag0z","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The un-dead’s intensely concentrated aura of unholiness infects the PC with an unholy aura. Any magical blessings or similar effects are automatically cancelled, and the character takes [[/roll 1d4]] points of temporary Personality loss.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[23,23],"drawn":false},{"_id":"EJhJ9tMQEa9xH8CH","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Grave rot! The wound bubbles and festers like a thing not from this earth. The rot causes an additional [[/roll 1d12]] damage and [[/roll 1d6]] Strength loss immediately, and the wound will not heal naturally. The damage and Strength loss can only be recovered via magical healing.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[24,24],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Hn3BkfX4qAwhAmxg","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"In a supernatural display, flesh melts away from the wound, revealing the bones beneath and causing an additional [[/roll 1d6]] damage and 1 point of Stamina loss. Each round thereafter, the radius of melted flesh expands, causing an additional  [[/roll 1d6]] damage 1 point of Stamina loss. The melting flesh continues to expand until the PC dies. It can only be suspended via magical healing with a spell check of 20 or greater.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[25,25],"drawn":false},{"_id":"42mOugGmjat5e49S","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Death rattle! The stench of un-death chokes the character, who collapses in a fit of gagging that slowly begins to suffocate him. He must make a DC 20 Fort save or lose [[/roll 1d4]] points of Stamina. If he fails the Fort save, he must make another save on the next round. If that fails, he takes additional Stamina damage and must make another save. The pattern continues until he makes a save or dies.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[26,26],"drawn":false},{"_id":"amOIHIkdHmESG85M","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The un-dead creature sucks life force from the character. The PC takes an additional [[/roll 1d20]] damage, and the un-dead creature heals that same amount (not to exceed its original total hit points).","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[27,27],"drawn":false},{"_id":"BeKTFYsEoz2GQokI","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The wizening. The character immediately ages [[/roll 1d20]] years. If the result is 15 or more, he permanently loses 1 point of Strength, Agility, and Stamina as his body weakens.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[28,28],"drawn":false},{"_id":"VGS3an7Vm0ktuvT6","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The end is always dust: the wounded area crumbles to dust, inflicting an extra [[/roll 2d12]] damage and permanently disfiguring the character. He loses the use of that arm, leg, hand, or whatever area was struck. On the following round, the area adjacent to the wound in turn crumbles to dust, inflicting an additional [[/roll 1d6]] damage. The radius of dust transformation continues to expand, inflicting an additional [[/roll 1d6]] damage each round until the character is dead. The transformation to dust can only be stopped by very powerful magic.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[29,29],"drawn":false},{"_id":"empHAltj0Nv23Jj7","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Un-death seeks un-death: in a flash of thick black smoke, the un-dead creature expends some of the necromantic energies that sustain it to transform the PC into un-death. The un-dead attacker automatically loses [[/roll 1d6]] hit points and may be killed as a result. The PC collapses in a state of apparent death, only to arise [[/roll 1d6]] rounds later as an un-dead creature under the control of the judge. Roll [[/roll 1d8]] to determine the type of creature that arises: (1-4) zombie, (5-6) skeleton, (7) ghoul, (8) ghost.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[30,500],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d30","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"Er2LfffNaI4tiVRD","name":"Crit Table II: All Thieves and Elves","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dcc-compendiums.dcc-criticial-hit-tables.8PGoMU3AhECoUJsy"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/robber.svg","description":"","results":[{"_id":"Ja5h3w31ERwwNDnW","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Miss! Hesitation costs you the perfect strike!","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-500,0],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wLFdOE3JqWHP3KPX","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike misses critical organs. Inflict a paltry +[[/roll 2d3]] damage with this strike.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"oH6BBBMa1dGo8H9Y","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Slashes to head removes foe’s ear. Inflict +[[/roll 1d6]] damage with this strike and leave the enemy with a nasty scar.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"akSsKMZMWOEWoQKK","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Clean strike to back. Inflict +[[/roll 2d6]] damage with this strike.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"4JzaAUimt8OJgVTX","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow to chest staggers foe. You can make an immediate free attack.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"XuqIMx48SS69gazN","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow pierces foe’s kidneys. Inflict +[[/roll 3d3]] damage with this strike, and the foe is stunned for 1 round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"uHvSN7JMyjbMuIpj","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe dazed by ferocious attack; his speed and actions are reduced by half.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"hE06fopHfr9iFmMW","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to chest grazes vital organ. Inflict +[[/roll 3d4]] damage with this strike.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"FkMyeajBm9onDH8U","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike cuts a line down foe’s face. He is blinded by blood for [[/roll 1d4]] rounds","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"ETyv8P11JmgzHnMm","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe stumbles over his own limbs, falling prone. Make another attack.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false},{"_id":"1fvNNOmB4fxtTqet","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Masterful strike! Inflict +[[/roll 2d6]] damage with this strike.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false},{"_id":"tnQBLpYnj6CGmkcU","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike severs larynx. Foe is reduced to making wet fish noises","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"rs0haeQsODdhDXtg","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Savage strike! Foe must succeed on a Fort save (DC 10 + PC level) or faint from the pain.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"kxJosmjoiJ9HiKU6","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Foe disoriented by quick strikes. Foe suffers a -4 penalty to attack rolls for [[/roll 1d4]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"SBMGNYn0LpuGrMmR","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to head. Foe must make a Fort save (DC 10 + PC level) or fall unconscious.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false},{"_id":"N4m0cnL0jNSdZOCd","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow drives foe to ground. Inflict +[[/roll 2d6]] damage with this strike, and the enemy is knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false},{"_id":"cxzSEf54hXfss0X1","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lightning-fast shot to the face pops the foe’s eye like a grape. Foe is permanently blinded in one eye and can take no actions for [[/roll 1d3]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false},{"_id":"NFAGzTFvD0uCpAdw","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike pierces lung. Inflict +[[/roll 2d6]] damage with this strike, and the foe can take only one action on his next turn.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"uvZ2jRwuSm3Webxa","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Devastating strike to back of head. Inflict +[[/roll 1d8]] damage with this strike, and the foe must make a Fort save (DC 10 + PC level) or fall unconscious.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false},{"_id":"eCYD4131cNrUEiDO","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Attack severs major artery. Inflict +[[/roll 1d10]] damage with this strike, and the foe must make a Fort save (DC 10 + PC level) or fall unconscious from shock and massive blood loss.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"8da9jd5WYUf22aOK","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Throat slashed! Inflict +[[/roll 2d6]] damage with this strike, and the foe must make a Fort save (DC 13 + PC level) or die in [[/roll 1d4]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false},{"_id":"T2fILYm61nGhAai0","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike pierces spinal column. Inflict +[[/roll 3d6]] damage with this strike, and the foe must make a Fort save (DC 15 + PC level) or suffer paralysis.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[21,21],"drawn":false},{"_id":"c2uwdLBb8s2ynvKm","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Chest skewered, spearing a variety of organs. Inflict +[[/roll 2d6]] damage with this strike, and the foe must make a Fort save (DC 13 + PC level) or die in [[/roll 1d4]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[22,22],"drawn":false},{"_id":"QMOIDT1juhiOw78E","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike through ear canal enters the brain. Ear wax instantly removed, and the foe must make a Fort save (DC 15 + PC level) or die instantly. Inflict an extra +[[/roll 2d6]] damage on successful save.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[23,23],"drawn":false},{"_id":"WuIyo5krDKTpixl3","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike through heart! Inflict +[[/roll 3d6]] damage with this strike, and the foe must make a Fort save (DC 20 + PC level) or die instantly.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[24,500],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"GYYB0eeW70VjFBdi","name":"Crit Table G: Giants","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dcc-compendiums.dcc-criticial-hit-tables.Qwf3X95nrY8abuTe"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/giant.svg","description":"","results":[{"_id":"yJ7TDgFhWMqmxAlk","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Crushing blow. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d8]] damage, and the character’s spine is compressed. The PC permanently loses [[/roll 1d6]]” of height.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-500,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"hdNWIcfK7ZThkBOo","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Broken arm. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d10]] damage and one arm is crippled. The character suffers permanent loss of 1 Strength (arm never heals back to original position properly), and the arm cannot be used until healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"OJRLEmakE4jdNtnV","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Broken leg. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d10]] damage and one leg is crippled. The PC suffers permanent loss of 5’ of speed (leg never heals properly) and moves at half speed until healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"PgFSydr2noHZs8Nx","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Crushed chest. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d12]] damage and chest is caved in. Until completely healed, any sort of exertion (including combat, running, swimming, jumping, etc.) requires DC 6 Fort save. Failure indicates permanent loss of 1 Stamina (due to several organ damage; e.g., heart attack, lung failure, etc.).","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"0nl4uX3twOLv1MtD","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Flattened. The PC is literally flattened into the ground by the sheer force of the blow, with multiple broken bones and several shattered ribs. The character takes an additional [[/roll 1d12]] damage and permanently loses 1 Stamina.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"3Zk66x4vltepse7s","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Ricochet blow. The giant’s staggering attack sends the target hurling through the air up to [[/roll 3d30]]’ to collide with another victim (randomly determined). Both the original target and the secondary target take [[/roll 1d10]] damage from the collision (in addition to the giant’s normal damage against the first target).","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"GrhbIII98Ijxjcwv","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Colossal head strike. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 2d6]] damage and the PC permanently loses 1 point of Intelligence. In addition, there is a 25% chance the character forgets the last 24 hours of his life.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"5TS35ZVYruo8yZSz","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Weapon smash. The giant’s massive blow causes an additional [[/roll 1d8]] damage and splinters the character’s weapons and equipment. The PC’s weapons and equipment each have a 50% chance of being destroyed; roll for each item: armor is busted loose (straps broken and plates dented), shields are shattered, weapons splintered or cracked, etc. Magic items are destroyed only 10% of the time instead of 50%.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"AsjPqN7TKjmz8Rhg","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Sweeping blow. The giant’s strike bowls over the character, and he takes an extra [[/roll 1d8]] damage and is knocked prone (must spend his next activation to stand). In addition, the giant can make another attack as long as it is directed against a different target, who must be within melee range and adjacent to the first target. If this second attack hits, the giant can attack another target, up to five in total, as it sweeps through its opponents.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false},{"_id":"1CxJihZwC7GNqevI","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Legs crushed into ground. The giant’s blow hits the PC square on the head, driving him into the earth like a nail into a board. The character takes an additional [[/roll 2d8]] damage, and both his legs are broken as he is propelled [[/roll 1d4]] feet into the earth (reduced to [[/roll 1d4]] inches if surface is stone). The character suffers a permanent loss of 10’ of speed and 1 Agility (legs never heal properly) and is temporarily reduced to a speed of 1’ (yes, one foot per round) until his two broken legs are healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false},{"_id":"shRYhiWLAUjOBJs2","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Roll again twice.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[11,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"nOn4htpm0VMBdc1b","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Roll again three times.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[13,500],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"Q3y4GbygjdrH54Jc","name":"Crit Table DR: Dragons","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dcc-compendiums.dcc-criticial-hit-tables.dGNRQNFTCVGd2zQx"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/dragon-head.svg","description":"","results":[{"_id":"pKHzLxjExI87lKJ1","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon rakes target with its spiny hide. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d6]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-500,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"DXhab0pSggInDD4e","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon crushes PC’s head between its jaws! The PC is stunned and falls to the bottom of the initiative count for remainder of battle.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"dNE1uSFTsZ5JEi74","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon smashes the PC’s legs, knocking the PC prone. The character suffers -5’ speed until healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"SgqNRc19SPUvRfjK","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon targets the character’s weapon. The character takes half damage, but must make an opposed Strength check against the dragon. Treat dragon as Strength equal to 10 + HD. If the check fails, dragon grabs weapon and hurls it [[/roll 3d10]]x10’ feet away.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"n68guSWoo1p3t1ZC","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow to shield arm! Normal damage and the shield is destroyed. If no shield, this attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d6]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Ocqx5BECbIIZaybn","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Scale, tooth, or claw lodged in the PC’s chest! This attack inflicts +[[/roll 2d6]] damage, plus an additional [[/roll 1d6]] damage next round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"HQhFfDtWnKE85Bnd","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Breath weapon splash! Spittle laced with dragon’s breath weapon causes an additional [[/roll 1d8]] damage and any other side effects of breath weapon (poison, sleep, etc.) if appropriate.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"gkoF6nEcdp896G3e","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Arm ripped from socket! Dragon hurls the arm away. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d12]] damage, and the arm is forever useless unless recovered and magically healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"5QNWMqHw3YHBM6Ng","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Tail-sling! Dragon wraps its tail around the PC and slingshots him into the distance. The character is flung [[/roll 3d6]]x10’ away in a random direction. If a wall or other obstruction is in the way, the character slams into it. The PC takes normal damage from the blow plus an additional [[/roll 1d4]] damage per 30’ (or portion thereof) he is thrown, plus an additional [[/roll 1d6]] if he hits a wall or obstruction.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false},{"_id":"6P13J9YcWwrlql9A","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Combination strike! Normal damage and the dragon follows up with a second attack of same type.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false},{"_id":"sfFCvW3Mo9ahZutd","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Claw through the throat! The PC can’t speak until healed and spends the next round struggling to breathe (unable to act).","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"WD44adtIXKe6sa58","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon targets the PC’s kneecap. PC’s movement cut by half and this attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d10]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"0uJtzz3VpmXmdsJy","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Awe-inspiring blow! This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d12]] damage, and all nearby retainers and henchmen are forced to make a morale check. Additionally, PCs must make a Will save (vs. DC of 10 + dragon’s HD) or take a -2 penalty to their remaining attacks this round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"IgwzLFmvmeQJRWDE","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Breath weapon combo attack! Dragon unleashes a tiny fraction of its power against the character. This does not count against its daily breath weapon use. The PC takes normal damage plus a breath weapon strike at half normal damage—in most cases this means half damage on a failed save and quarter damage on a save.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false},{"_id":"PnIXqwuCW5wFit31","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon spears the PC with one of its leg spines, then moves away. The PC flails about trying to free himself from impalement. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 2d12]] damage, and the PC can only free himself with a DC 16 Agility check. The PC can take no actions until freed, and moves with the dragon while impaled.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false},{"_id":"UX512zRg2csWymQ0","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon finishes its strike with a mighty head-butt! The character is sent flying [[/roll 2d4]]x10’ away from the dragon and takes an additional +[[/roll 3d6]] damage from the head-butt and subsequent fall.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false},{"_id":"QnjrPFQfhE3nHZSf","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon bends back the PC’s leg in a way it was never meant to, snapping the leg in half. The character’s movement is reduced by half, and he takes an extra [[/roll 2d6]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"4yxZzHZbym3vVqsl","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon pins the character down with one claw before slashing with another. Dragon inflicts +[[/roll 1d6]] damage and gets a bonus claw attack at +4 to hit.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false},{"_id":"QQJlqJnPBajfiKFZ","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Rag doll smash! Dragon locks onto the character’s ankle, swings him up, and smashes him to the ground head-first. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d16]] damage, and the PC must make a Fort save (DC 15 + HD) or fall unconscious.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"fFX34YFz9jTNcxeS","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon’s spines pierce the character in [[/roll 1d7]] places. Long, sharp, lance-like dragon scales emerge from the character’s back, piercing multiple important organs. The character takes double damage, and if he survives, he is automatically reduced to 1 Strength and 1 Agility as his organs fail one by one. However, the character is now stuck to the dragon (its head, claw, wing, or whatever part the dragon attacked with). The dragon must spend its next attack with that limb prying off the bleeding PC before it can use that attack mode again. Once the PC is pried off, he takes [[/roll 1d8]] damage per round from massive hemorrhaging. Only magical healing can arrest the bleeding and prevent death.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false},{"_id":"2eQ9qlKMCjc8qZ4e","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon hooks the PC with its wing and does a lift-and-smash. The character takes an additional +[[/roll 2d8]] damage and is automatically stunned for [[/roll 1d4]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[21,21],"drawn":false},{"_id":"mJtZ0PA9P4PsY4n0","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon captures the PC with its tail and begins constricting like an anaconda. The PC automatically takes an extra [[/roll 1d8]] crushing damage. Additionally, the PC is held in place and begins suffocating. The character must make a Fort save each round thereafter (DC equals 10 + dragon’s HD) or die of suffocation. The PC cannot escape (or move in any way) until he succeeds on an opposed Strength check (treat dragon as 10 + HD). The dragon cannot use its tail to attack while holding PC","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[22,22],"drawn":false},{"_id":"MIEAyoVAFGPW9iNN","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon uses one claw to hold down the PC while it rips his limbs off with the other. The character loses [[/roll 1d3+1]] limbs, taking an extra [[/roll 1d14]] damage for each limb lost. The result is probably a paraplegic or quadriplegic PC. The dragon proceeds to swallow the limbs. Limbs can only be restored if they are recovered from the dragon’s gullet and then magically reattached.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[23,23],"drawn":false},{"_id":"FSxRATLPSeUYGyQq","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Dragon embeds its claw/tooth/spine in the PC and shreds the character’s internal organs. The character takes an additional [[/roll 1d16]] damage and is pinned in place, unable to take any action. On the following round, the dragon finishes this attack by ripping out the character’s guts. The character is disemboweled. The character automatically dies in [[/roll 1d4]] rounds as he bleeds out. The dragon proceeds to hurl the character’s internal organs at another opponent, forcing a DC 20 morale check.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[24,24],"drawn":false},{"_id":"7jjDvD1viHBDEzPT","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"With staggering precision, the dragon plucks out both the character’s eyes in a single strike. The character takes no additional damage but is permanently blinded. The dragon flings the eyeballs back at the PC, who, in his now-sightless state, fails to see them go rolling out of reach.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[25,25],"drawn":false},{"_id":"aLXBM2O3Qsnd4hb5","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The dragon swallows the character whole in a single massive bite. The character takes normal damage and is now trapped in the dragon’s gullet. The character automatically takes an additional [[/roll 3d8]] damage each round thereafter from suffocation, constriction, and stomach acids. If the character succeeds in a DC 22 Strength check he can force his hands to move against the crushing strength of the dragon’s stomach, allowing an attack of some kind (e.g., drawing a dagger to try to cut his way out), but he cannot be freed until the dragon is killed and he is cut out.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[26,26],"drawn":false},{"_id":"SN86ZsCyXoCVJi3o","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The dragon’s razor-sharp talons (or teeth or spines, as appropriate) slash the character in perfect synchronicity, rendering the character’s body into equal thirds. Instant death!","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[27,27],"drawn":false},{"_id":"9g6aRvd9h2bFt7on","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Practicing a difficult draconic maneuver, the dragon executes a “reverse breath weapon,” breathing out in a short burst then immediately inhaling. This focused attack does not count against the dragon’s daily breath weapon use. The PC takes normal damage, plus a full breath weapon hit (with a normal save allowed). There is no area of effect, as the dragon immediately cuts off the breath weapon after a microsecond of attack.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[28,28],"drawn":false},{"_id":"07VfkBPyElSve4Qd","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The dragon pins the character down, cracks his rib cage open, reaches into his chest cavity, and rips out his heart. The character dies instantly. Brandishing the heart as a bludgeoning weapon, the dragon then makes one free claw attack against the nearest ally of the PC, splattering the character’s heart on the ally.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[29,29],"drawn":false},{"_id":"DiqdPFBxSNuPxR6D","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The dragon explodes the character’s head into splinters with an incredible blow, causing instant death. Everyone who witnesses the attack must make a morale check vs. DC 25 or flee (for retainers) or remain stunned and motionless on their next round (for PCs). The dragon makes a free claw attack against the nearest PC, and may continue making additional claw attacks until it misses.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[30,500],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d30","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"TCbqZHYTwnE5HB0s","name":"Crit Table M: Monsters","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"RollTable.dn7RoX8BJV9KK9RC"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/troll.svg","description":"","results":[{"_id":"53a8VqTE0Nk8vf7Q","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to chest, breaking ribs. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d6]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-50,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"agko5rNYROJ0NLiv","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Stunning blow! The PC falls to the bottom of the initiative count for the remainder of the battle.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"yXwTJTPF3g6yV3KL","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Legs knocked out from beneath the character, knocking him prone.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"UHeCsknlTZKg5L28","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"PC disarmed. Weapon lands [[/roll 1d12+5]]’ away.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"aOyIZpcKHH3rY7my","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow to shield arm! If no shield, this attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d6]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"djIdOVp2CU3moPD4","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Weapon lodged in PC’s chest! This attack inflicts +[[/roll 2d6]] damage and an additional [[/roll 1d6]] damage next round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"v37YlicKfbpndL6M","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow to jaw! The PC loses [[/roll 1d8]] hp and the same number of teeth.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"QbS0UYrjXamw37e3","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow shatters PC’s forearm. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d6]] damage, and the arm is useless until healed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"B287pRQQOuh8SLGj","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to helm! If no helmet, this attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d8]] damage and forces a Fort save (DC 10 + HD). On a failed save, the PC falls unconscious.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false},{"_id":"7W5JNNSVWwvSNc76","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Stunning blow! The world spins as the fell monster makes a second attack!","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false},{"_id":"J9kTzd69CDoGZyeK","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to throat! The PC can’t speak until healed and spends the next round struggling to breathe.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"b5iua61su02czN28","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow smashes PC’s kneecap. The character’s movement is cut by half and this attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d10]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"UImcWXuLsuvS3IWj","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Crushing blow! This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d12]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"au4oH5MCcAMT4dgK","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"PC’s weapon sundered in the violent assault.*","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false},{"_id":"7xCvYm0qIn4NJdn0","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike to torso crushes internal organs. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d12]] damage, and force the PC to make Fort save (DC 15 + HD) to remain conscious through the pain.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false},{"_id":"8VN9WQ7BaxHkNKD9","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Devastating strike! This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d16]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false},{"_id":"aiVrWqfgV7nXm69Q","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"PC’s Achilles tendon is torn, snapping back into his thigh. The character’s movement drops to 5’ and the screaming can be heard for leagues.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"miu4IDOYVCTuWqu2","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Monster seizes PC by the neck. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d12]] damage and the monster makes a second attack at +4 to hit.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false},{"_id":"47ina6pyb6S3rICA","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Blow to cranium! This attack inflicts +[[/roll 1d16]] damage and the PC must make a Fort save (DC 15 + HD) or fall unconscious.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"HscE6kMcJmYzbnoj","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Terrifying blow pierces several important organs. The PC spends the next [[/roll 1d4]] days dying a slow, painfuldeath. Powerful magic (healing by a cleric of level 3 or higher) can arrest the dying.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false},{"_id":"UYZhy50u6wBpS9Qu","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Strike crushes skull, destroying the optic nerve and resulting in instant, permanent blindness.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[21,21],"drawn":false},{"_id":"HHgBvLG0YB3N8Dtf","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"PC’s leg is shorn from his body. The character cannot move. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 2d12]] damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[22,22],"drawn":false},{"_id":"xBAV5vEzNbF0eAfG","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Both the PC’s arms are torn from his body. This attack inflicts +[[/roll 3d12]] damage. Exceptionally cruel monsters may proceed to use PC’s arms as weapons.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[23,23],"drawn":false},{"_id":"AZXwFtPlUxzhUJ55","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"